<DESCRIPTION>
	<PARA> all interactive drawing using tools are derived from this base class. All mouse and key events on the canvas/client window are redirected to this class, via the ToolControl class. The tool derived from this base class, defines what needs to be done with the events.</PARA>
</DESCRIPTION>





